{"tid":1984340,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街抄switch 狗","createTime":"2020-04-22T11:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T12:47:54.000Z","uid":217344,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3264b44b184b8c94caed7e5263bda1ce9bc81605","tid":1984340,"uid":217344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，啱啱去完黃金走一轉，想買部Switch來玩下，就已經見到佢抄價都要2880左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都算啦，原先都打算照買來玩，真係想買嘅時候先知佢地全部都好賤格一定要你捆綁機套同埋Mon貼 (加多$380)，唔捆綁就唔俾單買主機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一睇機套同mon 貼，仆街啦DLLM 你啲機套同mon 貼咪又係大陸貨，即場上淘寶睇，一睇價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtvNm37.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtvNm37.png&h=9f2dd11c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AntK8J9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAntK8J9.png&h=78bf5b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDLGH，啲人已經夠慘要俾你食抄價，仲要捆綁貴超過10陪嘅機套mon 貼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最on9 有一間仲焗你買三百幾蚊嘅32G記憶卡<br />\n<br />\n我又唔係真係急住玩，一於等誠哥出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街爭氣啲啦！等佢地炒燶啲貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc9fb3e8db471c78b7e0a37c6f2d1de0a82f457","tid":1984340,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"我以為係抄款山寨機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7a8f9fec117e4cebb5c7208369ab73d2135ce9","tid":1984340,"uid":147489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"2020仲有人去黃金買機"},{"pid":"ae44bd563790fed05e13f